== Overview ==

Dragon Quest III for SNES features the Hero, three customizable party members, and temporary characters. This page documents all characters and their statistics.

== Character Data Structure ==

Each character is 64 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00-$07 || 8 || Name (6 characters + padding)
|-
| $08 || 1 || Class ID
|-
| $09 || 1 || Level
|-
| $0A-$0B || 2 || Current HP
|-
| $0C-$0D || 2 || Max HP
|-
| $0E-$0F || 2 || Current MP
|-
| $10-$11 || 2 || Max MP
|-
| $12 || 1 || Strength
|-
| $13 || 1 || Agility
|-
| $14 || 1 || Vitality
|-
| $15 || 1 || Intelligence
|-
| $16 || 1 || Luck
|-
| $17 || 1 || Attack
|-
| $18 || 1 || Defense
|-
| $19 || 1 || Personality ID
|-
| $1A-$1D || 4 || Experience
|-
| $1E-$3F || 34 || Equipment, spells, status
|}

