== Class Change ==

Available at Dharma Temple after Hero reaches level 20:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Class !! Can Change To
|-
| Hero || Cannot change
|-
| Warrior || Any except Hero/Sage
|-
| Martial Artist || Any except Hero/Sage
|-
| Mage || Any except Hero, Sage with Book
|-
| Priest || Any except Hero, Sage with Book
|-
| Merchant || Any except Hero/Sage
|-
| Gadabout || Any including Sage (free)
|-
| Thief || Any except Hero/Sage
|-
| Sage || Any except Hero
|}

'''Class Change Effects:'''
* Level resets to 1
* Stats halved (rounded down)
* Learned spells retained
* Equipment slots change

